	.string "{CREATE_MUGSHOT MUGSHOT_SUNRISE_LITTLE_GIRL EMOTE_NORMAL}I'm here with my mama!\p"
	.string "The music lady's nice!$"

ChiiTown_PokemonCenter_EventScript_Mom_Text_0:
